# The service role key is SECRET — never put VITE_ prefix on this one,
# and never commit it. It's only used by the small local API server
# (see server/ folder) so it's never bundled into the browser app. The
# browser never talks to Supabase directly — all reads and writes go
# through the Express API, which is why no anon key is needed here.
